data.description: This beautiful home is the perfect place to call your own. Fresh interior paint and partial flooring replacement in some areas provide a natural color palette throughout the property. The kitchen is complete with a center island to make meal prep a breeze. The flexible living space offers plenty of room to make it your own. The primary bathroom features double sinks, a separate tub and shower, and good under sink storage. Step outside and enjoy a fenced in backyard, complete with a covered sitting area for outdoor entertaining. This home is sure to check all the boxes and is ready for you to move in. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
